PrecisAppointment of HELEN MAMAYAOK MAKSAGAK of Cambridge Bay, Nunavut, to be Deputy Commissioner of Nunavut to execute the office and functions of the Commissioner during her absence or illness or other inability or when the office of Commissioner is vacant, for a term of three years.
